             was indicted for <rs id="t18211024-66-off388" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18211024-66-off388" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18211024-66-off388" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18211024-66-cd389" type="crimeDate">22d of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18211024-66-off388 t18211024-66-cd389"></join>, one watch, value 30 s.; two seals, value 1 s., and one key, value 6 d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18211024-66-victim651" type="victimName">
                           Benjamin 
                           Ackers
                        <interp inst="t18211024-66-victim651" type="surname" value="Ackers"></interp>
